This repository uses the same split-license model as `cwensel/rdr`, separating
workflow documentation from executable code:

| What | License | File |
| --- | --- | --- |
| **Methodology & documentation** — the Kata Flight process and all prose: `README.md`, `ARCHITECTURE.md`, `SKILLS.md`, `RESEARCH.md`, `workspace.example`, `*.template` documentation, and the instructional prose inside each `skills/*/SKILL.md` | [CC BY-SA 4.0](https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/) | [LICENSE-DOCS](LICENSE-DOCS) |
| **Code** — shell scripts, `*.sh.template`, plugin/marketplace JSON manifests, and any other source code | MIT | [LICENSE-CODE](LICENSE-CODE) |

